Downloads multiple Parameter Configurations from the mlrHyperopt servers

Retrieve the Paramater Configurations for the given ids from the mlrHyperopt servers.

downloadParConfigs(ids)

Arguments

ids
[character] One ore more unique identifiers of the Parameter Set

Value

[List of ParConfigs]

Examples

par.configs = downloadParConfigs(c("8","29"))
print(par.configs)
